<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.10.7">
<l>oḷḷiya karumañ ceyvaṉeṉ ṟuṇarnta māvali vēḷviyil pukku</l>
<l>teḷḷiya kuṟaḷāy mūvaṭi koṇṭu tikkuṟa vaḷarntavaṉ kōyil</l>
<l>aḷḷiyam poḻilvā yiruntuvāḻ kuyilka ḷariyari yeṉṟavai yaḻaippa</l>
<l>veḷḷiyār vaṇaṅka viraintaruḷ ceyvāṉ tiruveḷḷi yaṅkuṭi yatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple of the one who, having entered the sacrifice of Māvali</l>
<l rend="indent">who decided, “I will perform virtuous deeds,’ </l>
<l>As a wise dwarf, taking three steps, grew to reach [all] directions,</l>
<l>Is that very one - Tiruveḷḷiyaṅkuṭi where the lord quickly granted grace</l>
<l rend="indent">when Veḷḷiyār bowed,</l>
<l>As cuckoos which live [there], staying in the lovely cool groves,</l>
<l rend="indent">called, ‘Hari, Hari!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
